
& economy
 
 >> Help: Economy
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 The Frontier has a special economy that you need to know in order to excel
 your character with firepower, skills, and other important gameplay
 information.
 
 Categories:
 -----------
 Buy_Skills_Advantages		Unit_Purchasing			Limted_Units
 Placing_Bounties			Currency				PL (Purchase List)
 Playing_Lottery
 
 To see economy-related commands, type 'help economy-commands'.
 
 For a detailed look at these categories, see our online documentation:
 http://docs.btmux.com/index.php/Site_Frontier
 
